resistant 5 mg per poundoverdosage pyrantel pamoate moderate margin safety doses approximately 7 times recommended 25 mg per pound generally resulted toxic reactions signs overdose could include panting staggering loss balance contact veterinarian immediately notice signs cases accidental overdoseshelf life this product shelf life 3 years stored controlled room temperature i wouldn give
